{
  "stem": "734.5",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And I even got some people-- I set them in contact with, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] with some people who were instrumental in getting weapons in Europe.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And I think they got quite a few things out of those, out of that source-- captured, German captured weapons, which were controlled at that time by the French occupation forces.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 35,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "So that was a good opportunity at the time, while I was able to, to help along.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In June of '47, yeah.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, this came later.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "June '47, when I first arrived, I, I decided to go to school.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I could not go full time, because I had no-- I had to work, of course.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I did take some courses and wherever I could for the journalism, photography, et cetera.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Between the New School and School of Visual Arts, wherever I was able to squeeze in a course, which helped me.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I did work at a photography studio in New York City for a while, until I was drafted in the army.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I was drafted in January, '49.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] did the army.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And while I was in the service, I had an opportunity once to photograph General Omar Bradley, who came down to Fort Benning in Georgia for some special occasion.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was the time when magazine was trying to get him, because he needed a picture of him for an upcoming overseas addition, a cover shot.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And they couldn't get to him because he was in Fort Benning, tied up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And I was-- photographers were not allowed into Fort Benning at that time, to photograph this whole situation.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "So the Atlanta Bureau Chief of approached me, because I was assigned to do the job for the service, for the army.",
      "word_count": 22
    }
  ],
